		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			In my experience, you get the more experience if you perform the quests that are meant for your class.  With this in mind, if you are a Ranger, you will probably want to give the Tonics to Trantor Everhot, since he is the guy you must give them to for the Trueshot Longbow quest.  Since Groflah Steadirt is an Important NPC for Paladins, it would probably be better exp to give Tonics to him for exp.  For the rest of the classes, I can't say which would be better.
			</font>
	
		</td>
